                      "text": "<h2>What Will I Study?</h2>\n<p>This course offers you a challenging and stimulating introduction to the expanding field of media. </p>\n<p>During the course you will meet media professionals, work on client-prepared briefs and visit working media studios. You will develop the vital skills needed to work in a range of media related areas, including:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Television</li>\n<li>Film</li>\n<li>Advertising</li>\n<li>Radio</li>\n</ul>",
