                {
                  "value": {
                    "dtgeContentTypeAlias": "widgetRTE",
                    "value": {
                      "name": "Rich Text Editor",
                      "text": "<h2>What could I do next?</h2>\n<p>The creative industry is one of the UK’s most successful business sectors. You could progress to study a relevant degree at university, find employment, or start an Apprenticeship in the industry.</p>\n<p>You could work in areas such as: Media Production, Marketing and PR</p>\n<p>Degree subjects at university include: Television or Radio Broadcasting, Animation, Advertising.</p>",
